statement.tex:
\text{Find all points of discontinuity of f,\\
where f is defined by }\\

f(x) = \begin{cases} 
          x^3- 3,&if\, x \leq 2\\
          x^2+1,&if \, x\gt 2 \\
          \end{cases}

step.reason:
\text{For a function to be continuous at a\\
point it's limits on either sides should be\\
equal to the value of f(x) at that point}
